Attested since the {{w|Northern and Southern dynasties|Northern and Southern dynasties period}}. According to {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}}, the word may be much older as the graph already appeared in Zhou texts and was intended to mean "branch" (with {{zh-l|*木}} radical).

